<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf12bba2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10145"><num value="10145">§ 10145.</num><heading> Termination of certain provisions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Sections 10139 and 10140 of this title shall cease to have effect at such time as a repository developed under this part is licensed to receive and possess high-level radioactive waste and spent nuclear fuel.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf12bba3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/tI/s125">Pub. L. 97–425, title I, § 125</ref>, <date date="1983-01-07">Jan. 7, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/2229">96 Stat. 2229</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
